<subSubSection pageId="21" pageNumber="472" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="21.[151,1436,1333,1504]" pageId="21" pageNumber="472">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1369,1395]" pageId="21" pageNumber="472">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Souza, L. S. &amp; Pimenta, A. D." box="[324,621,1369,1396]" pageId="21" pageNumber="472" pagination="425 - 442" refId="ref37037" refString="Souza, L. S. &amp; Pimenta, A. D. (2019 b) Taxonomy of littoral Melanella (Gastropoda: Eulimidae) from Brazil, with comments on the Eulima species described by Verrill and Bush (1900). Marine Biodiversity, 49 (1), 425 - 442. https: // doi. org / 10.1007 / s 12526 - 017 - 0825 - x" type="journal article" year="2019">Souza &amp; Pimenta (2019b)</bibRefCitation>
discussed the shell morphology of the 
<typeStatus box="[1071,1119,1370,1396]" pageId="21" pageNumber="472">type</typeStatus>
species in detail. A concise diagnosis of the genus is doubtful since 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bowdich" authorityYear="1822" box="[612,726,1405,1431]" class="Gastropoda" family="Eulimidae" genus="Melanella" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="21" pageNumber="472" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[612,726,1405,1431]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="472">Melanella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
comprises a wide variety of species (
<bibRefCitation author="Bouchet, P. &amp; Waren, A." box="[1157,1431,1405,1431]" pageId="21" pageNumber="472" pagination="299 - 576" refId="ref32770" refString="Bouchet, P. &amp; Waren, A. (1986) Revision of the northeast Atlantic bathyal and abyssal Aclididae, Eulimidae, Epitoniidae (Mollusca, Gastropoda). Bollettino Malacologico, Supplemento 2, 299 - 576. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 140762" type="journal article" year="1986">Bouchet &amp; Warén 1986</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Souza, L. S. &amp; Pimenta, A. D." box="[151,429,1441,1468]" pageId="21" pageNumber="472" pagination="425 - 442" refId="ref37037" refString="Souza, L. S. &amp; Pimenta, A. D. (2019 b) Taxonomy of littoral Melanella (Gastropoda: Eulimidae) from Brazil, with comments on the Eulima species described by Verrill and Bush (1900). Marine Biodiversity, 49 (1), 425 - 442. https: // doi. org / 10.1007 / s 12526 - 017 - 0825 - x" type="journal article" year="2019">Souza &amp; Pimenta 2019b</bibRefCitation>
). Here, we follow previous authors in considering a great diversity in shell morphology in the present genus.
</paragraph>
